# ==============================================================================
# GITATTRIBUTES: TEXT ENCODING & BINARY ASSET MANAGEMENT
# ==============================================================================

# Force UTF-8 encoding for all Markdown files to preserve Arabic/English text integrity
*.md text eol=crlf
*.tex text eol=crlf
*.html text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# Treat Microsoft Office and PDF documents as strict binary files
*.docx binary
*.doc binary
*.pdf binary

# Treat Image Assets as strict binary files
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.png binary
*.svg text